      "content": "but i don't want to go back to the doctor just for another blood test. if i really ramp up the garlic and the greens, like eating a big salad with kale every single meal and taking a high dose garlic pill twice a day, can't that just keep my blood thin enough naturally? it seems safer than dealing with all those chemicals in the pills.",
